trans-unit.source: Enumerates the elements of an <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Enumera gli elementi di un <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: To get an IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A> method of an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.
trans-unit.target: Per ottenere un IRemoteArgumentDictionaryEnumeratorContract, utilizzare il <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A>metodo di un <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract.GetEnumeratorContract%2A>

trans-unit.source: Returns the key and the value of the current <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"></xref> entry.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce la chiave e il valore dell'oggetto corrente <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentDictionaryContract"> </xref> voce.

trans-unit.source: After an enumerator is created or after the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> method is called, the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> method must be called to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before calling the GetEntry method; otherwise, the return value of GetEntry is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Dopo la creazione di un enumeratore o dopo il <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>metodo viene chiamato, il <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>metodo deve essere chiamato per passare l'enumeratore al primo elemento della raccolta prima di chiamare il metodo GetEntry; in caso contrario, non è definito il valore restituito di GetEntry.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>

trans-unit.source: GetEntry also throws an exception if the last call to <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> returned `false`, which indicates the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: GetEntry genera anche un'eccezione se l'ultima chiamata a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>restituito `false`, che indica la fine della raccolta.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: GetEntry does not move the position of the enumerator, and consecutive calls to GetEntry return the same object until either <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A> or <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: GetEntry non modifica la posizione dell'enumeratore, le chiamate successive a GetEntry restituiscono lo stesso oggetto finché non <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>o <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A>viene chiamato.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.Reset%2A> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IRemoteArgumentEnumeratorContract.MoveNext%2A>
